<h1>Burns Depression Checklist</h1>

<p>Instructions: indicate how much you have
experienced each symptom during the past week, including today.
Please answer all 25 items.</p>

<ul>
  <li>0 = Not at all</li>
  <li>1 = Somewhat</li>
  <li>2 = Moderately</li>
  <li>3 = A lot</li>
  <li>4 = Extremely</li>
</ul>

